Get history data on a user

fpl_get_user_history.Rd

Retrieve an FPL user's history data, obtained via the user entry history endpoint.

fpl_get_user_history(user_id)

Arguments

user_id

user ID (found in a user's team page URL on the main FPL site).

Value

a tibble

Examples

fpl_get_user_history(user_id = 3808385)
